/*Callable Java class - MyCallable.java*/

List<Callable> ready = new ArrayList<Callable>();
ExecutorService executor = Executors.newFixedThreadPool(***.size())

for(String s: hostList){
  ready.add((new Callable());
}

List<Future<String>> allReturned = executor.invokeAll(ready);
executor.shutdown();

Same for runnable - except runnable won't return anything. 
